      "title": "Moderna vs. Recursion: Which Cutting-Edge Pharma Stock Is a Better Buy in 2026?",
      "summary": "Moderna and Recursion Pharmaceuticals represent two distinct approaches to biotech innovation: Moderna leverages proven mRNA technology with diversifying pipeline into oncology and rare diseases, while Recursion uses AI-driven drug discovery. Despite both operating at losses, Moderna is favored for 2026 due to its established revenue base and proven formula, whereas Recursion remains in earlier development stages with revenue expected to decline due to lower milestone payments.",
